      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 10, United States Code, to require the Secretary of the Army to establish a combat service recognition ribbon, similar to the Navy Combat Action Ribbon, to recognize participation in combat by members of the Army, regardless of branch.</title>
